<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #dfefff, #fff6f0);
      color: #333;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 8rem;
      margin: 0;
      color: #ff7b54;
    }

    h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    a.button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #ff7b54;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    a.button:hover {
      background-color: #ff5722;
    }

    .illustration {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>404</h1>
    <h2>Lost in Paradise?</h2>
    <p>Oops! The page you're looking for doesn't exist.<br>
    But don't worry, your next adventure is just a click away.</p>
    <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2972/2972185.png" alt="Travel Icon" class="illustration" width="150">
    <br>
    <a href="/" class="button">Back to Home</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
